; Quantumult X Fast rewrite remote resource for YouTube.
; Optimized for direct YouTube usage with lower startup overhead.
; Keeps: ad removal, background play, picture-in-picture.
; IMPORTANT: add `udp_drop_list = 443` to the main profile [general] manually.

hostname = *.googlevideo.com, youtubei.googleapis.com, youtubei-att.googleapis.com

^https:\/\/youtubei(?:-att)?\.googleapis\.com\/youtubei\/v1\/(browse|next|player|get_watch)(\?(.*))?$ url script-response-body https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bensontech1014/Quantumult-X-script/main/Script/Youtube/youtube.response.fast.js
^https?:\/\/[\w-]+\.googlevideo\.com\/initplayback.+&oad url reject-200
